FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776902564
OL,3,CStarmer's agreement to meet is
OL,4,C'significant' step, say Chinook crash
OL,5,Cbereaved
OL,7,FThe Wells and Mendip Hills MP said
OL,8,Fmore than 30 years on from the crash,
OL,9,Fbereaved families still want to know
OL,10,F"the reason why their loved ones were
OL,11,Fplaced on board an aircraft which,
OL,12,Faccording to the MoD's own test
OL,13,Fpilots, was described as 'positively
OL,14,Fdangerous'".
OL,16,FShe asked Sir Keir whether he would
OL,17,F"agree to meet the families, to
OL,18,Frebuild trust and to offer the
OL,19,Fpromised dialogue that the Ministry of
OL,20,FDefence clearly finds so difficult to
OL,21,Fachieve".
OL,26,@rD@AOUvD@KO]yD@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776902564
OL,3,CStarmer's agreement to meet is
OL,4,C'significant' step, say Chinook crash
OL,5,Cbereaved
OL,7,FIn response, the Prime Minister
OL,8,Fthanked her for raising the case, and
OL,9,Fsaid: "I will make sure that is looked
OL,10,Fat again in the light of what she has
OL,11,Fsaid, and that the families get the
OL,12,Frelevant meeting."
OL,14,FThe Chinook Justice Campaign, set up
OL,15,Fby the bereaved families, said it
OL,16,Fmarks the first time in more than 30
OL,17,Fyears they have been offered the
OL,18,Fopportunity to put their case directly
OL,19,Fto the Prime Minister.
OL,26,@qD@GOUtD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
