SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776902564
OL,3,CStarmer's agreement to meet is
OL,4,C'significant' step, say Chinook crash
OL,5,Cbereaved
OL,7,FJenni Balmer-Hornby, whose father died
OL,8,Fin the crash, said: "We are grateful
OL,9,Fto Tessa Munt MP for raising the
OL,10,FChinook case so powerfully in Prime
OL,11,FMinister's Questions today and
OL,12,Fensuring the voices of the families
OL,13,Fwere heard directly by the Prime
OL,14,FMinister.
OL,26,@pD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776902564
OL,3,CStarmer's agreement to meet is
OL,4,C'significant' step, say Chinook crash
OL,5,Cbereaved
OL,7,F"After more than three decades of
OL,8,Funanswered questions, the Prime
OL,9,FMinister's agreement to meet is a
OL,10,Fsignificant and welcome step."We hope
OL,11,Fthat meeting takes place as quickly as
OL,12,Fpossible, and marks the beginning of a
OL,13,Fmeaningful process to finally deliver
OL,14,Ftruth, transparency and accountability
OL,15,Ffor the families."
OL,17,FFor years, the pilots were wrongly
OL,18,Fblamed for the disaster before being
OL,19,Fformally cleared in 2011.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@^OUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
