OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776902564
OL,3,CStarmer's agreement to meet is
OL,4,C'significant' step, say Chinook crash
OL,5,Cbereaved
OL,7,FFamilies have continued to campaign
OL,8,Ffor full disclosure of all documents
OL,9,Frelating to the crash and for a judge-
OL,10,Fled public inquiry, arguing key
OL,11,Fquestions about the circumstances of
OL,12,Fthe disaster remain unanswered.
OL,14,FThe campaign said it now hopes the
OL,15,FPrime Minister's intervention will
OL,16,Fbreak the long-standing impasse, and
OL,17,Flead to a clear timetable for the
OL,18,Frelease of information and
OL,19,Fconsideration of a full independent
OL,20,Finquiry.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
